snippet.title: Sonic Shuffle Dreamcast Playthrough - My Precious... Precioustone
snippet.description:
Sonic Shuffle is a Sonic the Hedgehog-themed party game developed and published by Sega for the Dreamcast in 2000. 

Initial Release Date: November 14, 2000
Designer: Hidenori Oikawa

Developers: Sega, Sonic Team, Hudson Soft

Platform: Dreamcast

#gaming #marioparty #sonic
